Subject: Re: [T2] black crud coming off my 1970's steering wheel

The black stuff is probably the buildup of grime and skin oils on the
wheel.  It's normal.  Clean it off with a damp cloth, keeping the wheel
damp for an hour or so beforehand.

George Lyle

